  "title": "Personal Assistant (5 days)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Calendar &amp; Email</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage MD’s schedule and travel plans, coordinate with teams for alignment</li>\n  <li>Screen and respond to emails; draft replies or forward where needed</li>\n  <li>Handle calls and regional correspondence efficiently</li>\n  <li>Follow up on urgent tasks and ensure timely execution</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Meetings</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare agendas and materials, take notes, and track action points</li>\n  <li>Draft meeting minutes and ensure clear follow-through</li>\n  <li>Uphold strict confidentiality on all sensitive matters</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Communication</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Act as the MD’s primary liaison for staff and external contacts, including China team</li>\n  <li>Ensure smooth communication across all departments</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Documents</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain organized digital/physical files for quick access</li>\n  <li>Draft, proofread, and format letters, reports, and slides professionally</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Project Coordination</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Track project timelines and deliverables</li>\n  <li>Support cross-team collaboration and keep MD updated on progress</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
